7
00:04:29,353 --> 00:04:32,523
Now, she was guilty of three charges
against you:

8
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:35,984
depletion of the national treasury,

9
00:04:37,236 --> 00:04:41,740
conspiracy against the internal
