No.

13
00:04:58,173 --> 00:05:00,842
Mercy for the innocent.

14
00:05:00,843 --> 00:05:03,637
Mercy for the unfortunate.

15
00:05:04,137 --> 00:05:06,431
Mercy for humanity.

16
00:05:10,602 --> 00:05:14,523
An inescapable outcome
of democracy's connection

17
